OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1776265866
OL,3,CSouth East Water 'should have acted
OL,4,Cquicker' to deal with warning sign of
OL,5,Coutage
OL,7,FIn the most recent incident more than
OL,8,F24,000 homes in Tunbridge Wells lost
OL,9,Ftheir water supply with schools and
OL,10,Fcare homes disrupted in the lead-up to
OL,11,FChristmas.
OL,13,FIt was estimated that businesses lost
OL,14,Fa combined total of somewhere between
OL,15,F#10 million and #20 million because of
OL,16,Fthe crisis.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1776265866
OL,3,CSouth East Water 'should have acted
OL,4,Cquicker' to deal with warning sign of
OL,5,Coutage
OL,7,FThen thousands of properties in Kent
OL,8,Fand Sussex saw their supply disrupted
OL,9,Ffor days in January, with South East
OL,10,FWater (SEW) blaming the outage on
OL,11,FStorm Goretti causing burst pipes and
OL,12,Fpower cuts.
OL,14,FCustomers were left with no tap water,
OL,15,Funable to shower or bathe and could
OL,16,Fnot flush their toilets, while a
OL,17,Fnumber of schools were forced to close.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1776265866
OL,3,CSouth East Water 'should have acted
OL,4,Cquicker' to deal with warning sign of
OL,5,Coutage
OL,7,FLast month the regulator issued SEW
OL,8,Fwith a #22million fine for failures
OL,9,Fbetween 2020 and 2023 and launched a
OL,10,Ffresh investigation in January.
OL,12,FOn Tuesday Chief Executive of South
OL,13,FEast Water David Hinton, Chairman
OL,14,FChris Train and non-executive director
OL,15,FCaroline Sheridan are all appearing in
OL,16,Ffront of the committee.
OL,18,FThe Committee will later question
OL,19,Fchiefs of Ofwat, the Drinking Water
OL,20,FInspectorate and the Consumer Council
OL,21,Ffor Water.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1776265866
OL,3,CSouth East Water 'should have acted
OL,4,Cquicker' to deal with warning sign of
OL,5,Coutage
OL,7,FIn the second panel, witnesses will be
OL,8,Fasked to reflect on what the incidents
OL,9,Finvolving SEW mean in terms of reforms
OL,10,Fto the water sector.
OL,12,FAsked by Chair of the Committee,
OL,13,FAlistair Carmichael MP, Mr Hinton
OL,14,Frefused to give a mark out of 10 for
OL,15,Fthe company's handling of the water
OL,16,Foutages.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1776265866
OL,3,CSouth East Water 'should have acted
OL,4,Cquicker' to deal with warning sign of
OL,5,Coutage
OL,7,F"My expectation is that we deliver to
OL,8,Fall priority service customers and
OL,9,Fthat the bottled water stations are
OL,10,Fcompletely resourced the whole time,
OL,11,Fand customers can get access to
OL,12,Falternative water at all times.
OL,14,F"So whenever we do not meet that
OL,15,Fparticular yardstick, then I'm
OL,16,Fdisappointed."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUxD@NO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1776265866
OL,3,CSouth East Water 'should have acted
OL,4,Cquicker' to deal with warning sign of
OL,5,Coutage
OL,7,FThe chairman later revealed to the
OL,8,Fcommittee that chief executive David
OL,9,FHinton, who receives a #400,000
OL,10,Fsalary, has surrendered any bonus the
OL,11,Fboard may have chosen to pay him this
OL,12,Fyear.
OL,14,FHowever, MPs went on to repeatedly
OL,15,Fquestion Mr Train on why there had
OL,16,Fbeen no changes in the leadership
OL,17,Fteam, highlighting the major failings
OL,18,Fas well as criticism from the Prime
OL,19,FMinister, its shareholders, customers
OL,20,Fand a whole range of public and
OL,21,Fprivate bodies.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1776265866
OL,3,CSouth East Water 'should have acted
OL,4,Cquicker' to deal with warning sign of
OL,5,Coutage
OL,7,FAsked how bad performance would need
OL,8,Fto get to change the company's
OL,9,Fleadership, Mr Train said: "We have
OL,10,Flooked as you would expect us to do at
OL,11,Fwhat the appropriate leadership of the
OL,12,Forganisation is going forward.
OL,14,F"The board has given its commitment
OL,15,Fand its backing to Dave and the
OL,16,Fexecutive team going forward as the
OL,17,Fright solution for delivering what is
OL,18,Fbest for South East Water customers."
OL,26,@qD@\OUvD@AOUzD@eO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1776265866
OL,3,CSouth East Water 'should have acted
OL,4,Cquicker' to deal with warning sign of
OL,5,Coutage
OL,7,FHe added that the firm is "bolstering"
OL,8,Fthe executive with a number of
OL,9,Fexternal hires that will cover a
OL,10,F"broader spectrum of leadership across
OL,11,Fthe organisation".
OL,13,FPressed repeatedly on customers no
OL,14,Flonger having confidence in the
OL,15,Fcompany's leadership, he continued to
OL,16,Fdefend the team.
OL,18,FHe said: "We are accountable for where
OL,19,Fwe are. We as a board, we have to step
OL,20,Fback and ask the questions that you're
OL,21,Fasking.
OL,26,@oD@[OUoD@fO]rD@AOUsD@QO]zD@JOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1776265866
OL,3,CSouth East Water 'should have acted
OL,4,Cquicker' to deal with warning sign of
OL,5,Coutage
OL,7,F"We have to look at the broad context
OL,8,Fof the organisation.
OL,10,F"We have to look at the context of the
OL,11,Findustry and the sector and we have to
OL,12,Fdo what we think is best in the best
OL,13,Finterest of South East Water
OL,14,Fcustomers."
OL,16,FLabour MP Jenny Ridell-Carpenter said:
OL,17,F"We might be asking the right
OL,18,Fquestions but you're coming up with
OL,19,Fthe wrong answers."
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOUvD@KO]yD@AOU{D@SO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
