OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1776265866
OL,3,CSouth East Water 'should have acted
OL,4,Cquicker' to deal with warning sign of
OL,5,Coutage
OL,7,FIt comes after Ofwat announced in
OL,8,FMarch that it plans to fine SEW #22
OL,9,Fmillion over water supply failures
OL,10,Fbetween 2020 and 2023 impacting more
OL,11,Fthan 286,000 people.
OL,13,FThe watchdog said the firm "lacked
OL,14,Fownership" for fixing the root cause
OL,15,Fof supply failures and did not
OL,16,Fmaintain important infrastructure.
OL,26,@uD@\OUvD@JO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1776265866
OL,3,CSouth East Water 'should have acted
OL,4,Cquicker' to deal with warning sign of
OL,5,Coutage
OL,7,FIts investigation found that the
OL,8,Fcompany's response to these issues was
OL,9,F"slow and disorganised" and
OL,10,Fhighlighted shortages of bottled
OL,11,Fwater, saying said there were "not
OL,12,Fenough tankers or support for
OL,13,Fvulnerable customers".
OL,15,FMr Hinton was grilled by MPs in for
OL,16,Fhis company's handling of the November
OL,17,Fand December supply failure.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@WO]sD@_OUuD@UO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1776265866
OL,3,CSouth East Water 'should have acted
OL,4,Cquicker' to deal with warning sign of
OL,5,Coutage
OL,7,FBut days later, Mr Carmichael said he
OL,8,Fand his colleagues remained "deeply
OL,9,Fsceptical" about SEW's version of
OL,10,Fevents presented to MPs.
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
OL,26,@pD@]OUqD@JO]
